{"tid":2439080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭月娥︰未來12個月須完成本地立法以便選出新任特首","createTime":"2021-03-09T03:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T04:13:56.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8fc23f9a829bfa7611777f0090af32079027a6","tid":2439080,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥接受內地CGTN訪問，指未來12月內必須完成有關修改選舉制度的本地立法工作。她解釋，她的任期於明年6月結束，明年3月便要進行下一任行政長官的選舉工作，因此特區政府需於12個月內，根據人大決定進行本地立法過程，再就選舉作出安排，包括選民登記和確定投票日等。 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又指，全國人大有關完善香港選舉制度的決定，相信只是原則性和完善制度的重點，同時授權全國人大常委會根據決定，修改基本法附近一和附件二。她指按照人大副委員長王晨的說法，會有機制審核或證明候選人資格，以及是否符合愛國者標準，相信稍後的公布中，資格審核機制會起到重要的作用。 <br />\n<br />\n對於為何不是由特區政府提出修改選舉制度，林鄭月娥強調中央有權主動作出修改，當下香港環境緊迫，特區政府不能按照既定步驟進行，情況就如去年《港區國安法》出台時的情況，只能由中央出面。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2382208&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy0XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=e270bda8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382208</a>"},{"pid":"b7ee2950481104a446503a06e101fc189cea31e0","tid":2439080,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"立咩法<br />\n唔好再扮依法施政啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a45703389b9f36070107b5c777bc54cb0d25f8b","tid":2439080,"uid":366932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:08:50.000Z","msg":"委任算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd75e29bbbd604deff305218fd9953fc0334446","tid":2439080,"uid":187664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂 都係中央任命"},{"pid":"71d774d1d8f4770158b54764ed938b0cb334a291","tid":2439080,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"欽點算啦好煩<br />\n<br />\n選何君堯啦，我支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203caa57214172a812c3e54b3d013397aa779ea1","tid":2439080,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:09:38.000Z","msg":"立乜法都只係無字天書任佢嗡"},{"pid":"0f6c0f6f95947e5c84c359163d03981563b51002","tid":2439080,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"緊急法咪得"},{"pid":"c3a9a94a32f0c539dbe3a151be7f8c3e5954ba88","tid":2439080,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:11:04.000Z","msg":"假民主不如真獨裁<br />\n直接委任，出問題可以直接炒鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25792c64f7a06a86b0815857f744b67ca5d6f91c","tid":2439080,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:12:36.000Z","msg":"成個香港都俾你玩爛左啦，你鐘意點就點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b40527eff57d80d38557339c25f606c2c2d0a6","tid":2439080,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"得啦 你話邊個做咪邊個做wfc"}]}